* ''Last Night's Dream'' (Warner Bros. Records, 1968)
[[Muddy Waters]]
*''[[The Best of Muddy Waters]]'' (Chess, 1958)
* ''[[Folk Singer (album)|Folk Singer]]'' (Chess, 1964)
